Step 2: Login Docker to ECR
Inside EC2 run:
aws ecr get-login-password --region ap-south-1 | docker login --username AWS --password-
stdin your-repository-uri-without-/myweb
Example:
aws ecr get-login-password --region ap-south-1 | docker login --username AWS --password-
stdin 123456789012.dkr.ecr.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com
